MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping is to refresh the LCM Copay spread data from the EDM on a daily basis. It copies the EDM data changes in their table DWU_EDW.T_CLNT_PLAN_COPAY_SPRD_HIST into the GDX version of the same table, since the last time this process ran
MAPPING.NAME: m_SCD_RCIT_CLNT_COPAY_SPRD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Route input records to two outputs - INSERT and UPDATE, based on new flag. When New Flag =1then record is inserted into the target table When NewFlag= 0then record is updated into the target table
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: rtr_NewFlag_ChangeFlag

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
